cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a method for multimodal biometric identification using deep convolutional neural networks. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses fusion algorithms for multiple modalities, which could be considered as multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) categories. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on biometric databases, which could be considered as information retrieval (cs.IR) category.
